<h1 class="px-6 text-center mt-12 uppercase font-thin text-gray-500 text-xl tracking-widest">
  This is for you
</h1>

<div class="max-w-lg m-auto p-6">
  <ul class="ml-2">
    <% icon_classes = "mr-4 w-6 h-6 text-2xl text-gray-600 text-uniq flex-none flex items-center" %>
    <% item_classes = "flex mb-5 items-center" %>
    <li class="<%= item_classes %>">
      <div class="<%= icon_classes %> a-shake">
        📱
      </div>
      <span>
        You are <strong>building a digital product</strong> with users&nbsp;signing&nbsp;in.
      </span>
    </li>
    <li class="<%= item_classes %>">
      <div class="<%= icon_classes %> a-bow">
        🙌
      </div>
      <span>
        You <strong>care about privacy</strong> and want to start your relation with your customers the best possible way.
      </span>
    </li>
    <li class="<%= item_classes %>">
      <div class="<%= icon_classes %> a-turn">
        ☀️
      </div>
      <span>
        You can see the benefits from <strong>not handling authentication yourself</strong>.
      </span>
    </li>
    <li class="<%= item_classes %>">
      <div class="<%= icon_classes %> ">
        <div class="absolute">🌍</div>
        <div class="absolute globe position first">🌍</div>
        <div class="absolute globe position second">🌎</div>
        <div class="absolute globe position third">🌏</div>
      </div>
      <span>
        You believe <strong>the world deserves a better solution</strong> to centralized authentication. Perfectly free from commercial&nbsp;interests.
      </span>
    </li>
    <li class="<%= item_classes %>">
      <div class="<%= icon_classes %> a-zoom">
        🎁
      </div>
      <span>
        You want to <strong>contribute to basic authentication infrastructure</strong> by paying your fair amount based on usage.
      </span>
    </li>
  </ul>
</div>
